1. Default parameter values are not allowed for struct constructors in C#. They are only allowed for instance constructors of classes.

2. Initialization of `Vector3` and `Quaternion` with an empty constructor call may not work as expected. You need to provide valid values or use `new Vector3()` and `new Quaternion()`.

